Fixes
../qemu-6.2.0/linux-user/host/ppc64/../ppc/host-signal.h:16:32: error: incomplete definition of type 'struct pt_regs'
    return uc->uc_mcontext.regs->nip;
           ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~^

